# Dropbox Studio integration
#
# 1. Create a Dropbox app at https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
#    - API: Scoped Access
#    - Access type: Full Dropbox (or App folder)
#    - Permissions: files.content.read, files.content.write
#
# 2. Under OAuth 2 → Redirect URIs, add:
#    - http://localhost:5173/          (local dev)
#    - https://<your-gh-pages-url>/   (production)
#
# 3. Copy your App key below.

VITE_DROPBOX_APP_KEY=your_app_key_here
